{"word":"διαχωρίζω","slug":"διαχωρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διαχωρίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διά\">διά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χωρίζω\">χωρίζω</a></el>, for the idea of separation, as in <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χωρίς\">χωρίς</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Hom.\">Hom.</a> *<el>χῆτος</el> (only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a>) ‘want, lack’, and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χήρα\">χήρα</a></el>, as well as <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χώρα\">χώρα</a></el>] ‘cause separation’, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><i>go away, part, leave</i> <a href='B:490 9:33'>Lk 9:33</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διαχλευάζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διγαμία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}